11:27.208 --> 11:28.375
Okay?

11:35.041 --> 11:36.916
Then don't you ever disappear on me again.

11:57.750 --> 11:59.208
You're awake.

11:59.291 --> 12:00.916
Do you feel better?

12:02.083 --> 12:04.375
Let's go to the hospital later, okay?

12:06.541 --> 12:08.500
How did you find me?

12:08.583 --> 12:11.500
Come on. I'm Cream.

12:12.250 --> 12:13.916
I'll always find you.

12:20.458 --> 12:21.750
I'm warning you.

12:21.833 --> 12:24.000
You can't eat instant noodles,

12:24.666 --> 12:26.041
