12:38.416 --> 12:40.541
We'll stay together until we're very old.

12:40.625 --> 12:41.833
Won't we?

12:53.625 --> 12:54.666
Don't be afraid.

12:56.375 --> 12:57.625
I'll keep you company.

13:23.083 --> 13:24.083
K.

