most incredible lyrics for you.

14:14.916 --> 14:16.375
When A-Lin wins an award,

14:16.458 --> 14:17.916
everyone will know

14:18.000 --> 14:21.041
that K and Cream are the best duo.

14:38.875 --> 14:40.833
