14:43.083 --> 14:44.000
Don't worry.

14:45.083 --> 14:46.125
He's fine.

14:46.833 --> 14:48.708
He knows you're the only family I have.

14:50.125 --> 14:51.833
I have to take care of my family.

14:55.291 --> 14:56.416
Thank you.

15:00.416 --> 15:02.291
