15:29.916 --> 15:32.041
and a relationship so deep,

15:33.166 --> 15:35.958
that you can feel happiness

15:36.041 --> 15:37.958
and sadness at the same time.

15:43.750 --> 15:44.791
Po-han.

15:46.666 --> 15:48.541
Why did you want to become a musician?

15:53.416 --> 15:55.041
Because one day, I hope

15:57.166 --> 15:58.583
I can make a song

15:59.416 --> 16:01.125
and play it to the person I like.

16:05.916 --> 16:06.750
I see.

16:10.791 --> 16:12.708
I wrote a new song.

16:13.291 --> 16:14.208
Do you want to hear it?

16:23.833 --> 16:24.875
Yes.

16:53.958 --> 16:55.125
Delicious, right?

20:22.958 --> 20:28.666
G KEY "THE SADDEST THING"

