30:03.041 --> 30:05.291
Don't you think that sounds like a family?

30:08.916 --> 30:09.916
Family?

30:11.333 --> 30:12.375
Yes.

30:12.458 --> 30:13.500
Family.

30:14.041 --> 30:15.666
From now on,

30:15.750 --> 30:17.375
