32:07.083 --> 32:08.958
<i>I was all alone.</i>

32:11.791 --> 32:13.375
<i>But in my world,</i>

32:13.916 --> 32:15.708
<i>there are always two people,</i>

32:18.666 --> 32:21.333
<i>K and Cream.</i>

32:32.458 --> 32:34.583
