33:20.500 --> 33:22.875
<i>I can't imagine myself not loving him.</i>

33:25.916 --> 33:28.500
<i>Thank you, Bonnie.</i>

33:28.583 --> 33:29.625
Okay.

33:29.708 --> 33:32.500
<i>I wouldn't have finished the song
without your encouragement.</i>

33:35.250 --> 33:37.208
<i>Now that the song is finally done,</i>

33:38.083 --> 33:39.666
<i>I've fulfilled my promise with K.</i>

33:42.166 --> 33:43.208
<i>I have no regrets.</i>

33:48.750 --> 33:49.708
<i>K.</i>

33:50.500 --> 33:52.541
<i>I'm grateful to have met you in this life.</i>

33:55.708 --> 33:57.708
<i>Thank you for being my family.</i>

34:14.041 --> 34:15.333
<i>I'll find you</i>

34:16.625 --> 34:18.250
<i>in my next life.</i>

34:29.250 --> 34:30.208
Cream.

