<i>And it made me realize</i>

36:23.833 --> 36:26.416
<i>that things still exist
even if they disappeared.</i>

36:28.166 --> 36:31.416
<i>I believe K and Cream hoped</i>

36:31.500 --> 36:33.416
<i>that everyone who hears this song</i>

