36:49.916 --> 36:51.958
Who said that the saddest story

36:52.625 --> 36:54.333
can't have a happy ending?

37:05.166 --> 37:06.166
What's wrong?

37:07.541 --> 37:08.666
Nothing.

37:08.750 --> 37:09.916
-Let's go.
-Okay.

37:13.833 --> 37:14.875
Do you want to go to the beach?

37:15.375 --> 37:16.208
Sure.

37:22.958 --> 37:24.958
<i>I read this article before.</i>

37:25.041 --> 37:26.041
<i>It says</i>

37:26.125 --> 37:28.833
<i>the ocean separates us from the afterlife.</i>

37:29.791 --> 37:31.041
So if one day,

37:31.125 --> 37:32.916
when we're gone,

37:33.000 --> 37:35.708
a ferryman would carry us
to the end of the sea.

37:36.333 --> 37:37.541
That's the other side.

37:40.625 --> 37:44.166
After reading it,
I really wanted to go to the beach.

37:44.250 --> 37:46.375
I feel like when I get there,

37:48.125 --> 37:49.916
I'll find them.

37:51.125 --> 37:53.500
If you want to go, we'll go.

